<.decorative_heading tag="h3" style="simpler">Development</.decorative_heading>

<p>
  The site was built with WordPress and included integration with a third-party service the Valley of the Sun YMCA team used for their on-site scheduling. This allowed users to register for membership and manage their schedules without having to go to a physical location.
</p>

<p>
  The main pages I focused on during development due to their complexity and responsive needs were the homepage, the branch pages, and the myY pages, where users could login to view and manage their activities. The site features CSS animations, a mobile-friendly design, support for multiple languages, and a large number of unique page templates.
</p>

