<.decorative_heading tag="h3" style="simpler">Outcome</.decorative_heading>

<p>
  The new site made it easy for members to see what activities and classes were coming up without having to visit the physical branch. Between the new e-commerce website and the marketing campaign also handled by BIG YAM, Valley of the Sun YMCA saw an increase in walk-in traffic and registration by 42%.
</p>

<p>
  The Valley of the Sun YMCA website received an ADDY Award in 2015 for our responsive design work.
</p>

<p>The site has since been taken over by another agency.</p>
